    "start": 5888.169,
    "end": 5918.998,
    "text": "this as well. One of the, the big things when it comes to load growth is that you have to be able to quantify what exactly is happening and then what solutions you can come up with. So the audits that Luis was talking about earlier tonight are a key component of understanding what that load situation is, as well as how to rectify it. We can t make any decisions unless we know what the problem is and the granularity of that problem. So getting the information down first and be able to chart exactly what is happening within our city. It s critical to be able to make any"
